fields.history_note: Part of the Lovat Fraser Bequest (Misc.352/465-1978), bequeathed to the museum by Grace Lovat Fraser, widow of Claud Lovat Fraser the artist.  The initial basis of the collection was a group of Indian toys belonging to Lovat which he gave to Grace as an engagement present.
